== How to build k-means ==

    $ make

== How to run k-means on L0 ==

To run kmeans with input file input.file

    $ am run kmeans-stdin-to-pmem.bin input.file
    $ am run kmeans-from-pmem.bin

== Correctness tests ==

=== Tiny tests ===

Undefine

#define TINY_EXP

and `make` it again.

2 test cases:

Input: kmeans.input.tiny

Results:

4 6 4 100
100 8 4 4

Input: kmeans.input.tiny2

Results:

4 6 4 100
100 8 5 3

=== Small tests ===

Undefine 

#define SMALL_EXP

in kmeans.c

and `make` it again.

Get the input file:

    $ wget http://baijia.info/l0/kmeans.input.small.tar.bz2
    $ tar xf kmeans.input.small.tar.bz2

Input: kmeans.input.small

